data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, JAN 21ST 12PM - 3PM. Fantastic New build 2023, Open floor plan with LVP flooring throughout the first floor. Upgraded quartz countertops custom cabinets with soft close drawers and doors. Under cabinet lighting. Upgraded SS appliance package. Kitchen open to large living area. Butlers pantry between kitchen and formal dining room. Electric fireplace. Large primary suite with 2 walk in closets. En suite with soaking tub and oversized shower. 3 guest bedrooms with large hall bath with double vanity. Upstairs laundry. Large lot over quarter of an acre. Large fenced in backyard. 10 year structural warranty, 2 year septic warranty and 1 year well warranty all from builder as home was just built in 2023. Home centrally located just off Rt 17.
